<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Happy Learning - LMS Activation Mail</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            border: 2px solid black;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-image: url("https://i.pinimg.com/236x/99/35/b3/9935b305f2115385c38fd3f62098983b.jpg");
        }

        .email-header {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .email-body {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .activation-code {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-left: 8rem;
        }

        .activation-code-digit {
            border: 2px solid #007BFF;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #007BFF;
            margin: 0 5px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 50px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .email-footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1 style="color: #4CAF50;">ðŸŽ‰ Welcome to Happy Learning ðŸŽ‰</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello, ðŸ™‹ <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #4CAF50;"><%= user.name %></span>!</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with us. To activate your account, please use the activation code below:</p>
            <div class="activation-code">
                <% activationCode.toString().split('').forEach(function(digit) { %>
                    <div class="activation-code-digit">
                        <%= digit %>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
            <p>Please enter this activation code within five minutes to start your Happy Learning journey.</p>
            <p>If you did not register with us, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to <a href="mailto:jobforakash9770@gmail.com" style="color: #4CAF50;">contact us</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
